rn more contact howardl@insightba.net.)\r\n\r\nWe welcome your questions and suggestions. Use our <a title="Contact Us" href="/contact/">Contact Us</a> page to reach any one of us.', 'About Us', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '2-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-06-13 15:11:31', '2016-06-13 19:11:31', '', 2, 'https://insightba.net/2-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
