 (142, 1, '2016-06-13 10:38:27', '2016-06-13 14:38:27', '<span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">President &amp; CEO Howard Lancaster recognized a need for a more efficient, cost-effective way to deliver a higher level of third party administration services and benefit consulting.<strong>  Insight Benefit Administrators </strong>was formed.</span>\r\n\r\n<em>For our clients :</em>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">We offer a full menu of audit services for clients currently using TPA services. Leveraging our substantial expertise and experience, we can provide an objective review of plan administration, employee communications, compliance and more.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">We strive to:</span>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">actively seek feedback from your, our clients, your employees and the agent/broker community</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">continually evaluate product and service alternatives</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">to educate you and your employees</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">The Insight team approaches each covered member with caring, educational support and  experience while maintaining the highest ethical standards and confidentiality.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><em>For employees:</em> </span>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">Insight promotes freedom of opinion, ideas and expression; provides opportunities for professional growth; and is strives to maintain essential work-life balance.</span>\r\n\r\n<em>For the communities we serve: </em>Our social mission is to provide educational and financial support for pediatric dental care to underinsured and uninsured children.  (To learn more contact howardl@insightba.net.)\r\n\r\nWe welcome your questions and suggestions. Use our <a title="Contact Us" href="/contact/">Contact Us</a> page to reach any one of us.', 'About Us', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '2-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-06-13 10:38:27', '2016-06-13 14:38:27', '', 2, 'https://insightba.net/2-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
 (219, 1, '2016-06-29 08:52:31', '2016-06-29 12:52:31', 'Post-65 Medical Coverage\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Standard Medicare Supplement Coverage</li>\r\n 	<li>Medicare Advantage Coverage</li>\r\n 	<li>Group Retiree Insurance Medical Coverage (GRIP)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nPost-65 Prescription Coverage\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Employer Group Waiver Plan (EGWP) Coverage</li>\r\n 	<li>Fully Insured Group Prescription Coverage (PDP)</li>\r\n 	<li>Group Retiree Insurance Prescription (GRIP) Coverage</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nBilling and Enrollment\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Enrollment in Medical/Rx/Voluntary Programs</li>\r\n 	<li>Collection of retiree premium and employer stipends</li>\r\n 	<li>Reconciliation of employer monthly billings</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Retiree Products and Services', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '175-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-06-29 08:52:31', '2016-06-29 12:52:31', '', 175, 'https://insightba.net/175-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
 (220, 1, '2016-06-29 08:55:19', '2016-06-29 12:55:19', 'IBA evaluated carriers throughout the country that offer either replacement coverage to traditional Medicare Parts A &amp; B coverage or options to coordinate with traditional Medicare Parts A &amp; B coverage.  We chose to partner with carriers that demonstrate flexibility in plan design, provide top-notch service and deliver lower than average medical trend renewals. We formed partnerships with carriers that lower retiree premiums and stretch employer stipend dollars.\n\nIBA has access to several fully insured medical coverage carriers and options including:\n<ul>\n 	<li>Group medical coverage down to 2 lives</li>\n 	<li>Copay and coinsurance options</li>\n 	<li>Dental, Hearing and Vision options</li>\n 	<li>Holistic benefit options, such as Acupuncture and Chiropractic care</li>\n 	<li>Choice of Age Banded or Composite rating</li>\n</ul>\nImportant to those who travel, these programs offer freedom of choice with no network limitations and national access to providers and hospitals.', 'Post-65 Medical Products', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '182-autosave-v1', '', '', '2016-06-29 08:55:19', '2016-06-29 12:55:19', '', 182, 'https://insightba.net/182-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
 (221, 1, '2016-06-29 08:55:29', '2016-06-29 12:55:29', 'IBA evaluated carriers throughout the country that offer either replacement coverage to traditional Medicare Parts A &amp; B coverage or options to coordinate with traditional Medicare Parts A &amp; B coverage.  We chose to partner with carriers that demonstrate flexibility in plan design, provide top-notch service and deliver lower than average medical trend renewals. We formed partnerships with carriers that lower retiree premiums and stretch employer stipend dollars.\r\n\r\nIBA has access to several fully insured medical coverage carriers and options including:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Group medical coverage down to 2 lives</li>\r\n 	<li>Copay and coinsurance options</li>\r\n 	<li>Dental, Hearing and Vision options</li>\r\n 	<li>Holistic benefit options, such as Acupuncture and Chiropractic care</li>\r\n 	<li>Choice of Age Banded or Composite rating</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nImportant to those who travel, these programs offer freedom of choice with no network limitations and national access to providers and hospitals.', 'Post-65 Medical Products', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '182-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-06-29 08:55:29', '2016-06-29 12:55:29', '', 182, 'https://insightba.net/182-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
