 (180, 1, '2016-06-29 08:47:17', '2016-06-29 12:47:17', 'Post-65 Medical Coverage\n<ul>\n 	<li>Standard Medicare Supplement Coverage</li>\n 	<li>Medicare Advantage Coverage</li>\n 	<li>Group Retiree Insurance Medical Coverage (GRIP)</li>\n</ul>\nPost-65 Prescription Coverage\n<ul>\n 	<li>Employer Group Waiver Plan (EGWP) Coverage</li>\n 	<li>Fully Insured Group Prescription Coverage (PDP)</li>\n 	<li>Group Retiree Insurance Prescription (GRIP) Coverage</li>\n</ul>\nBilling and Enrollment\n<ul>\n 	<li>Enrollment in Medical/Rx/Voluntary Programs</li>\n 	<li>Collection of retiree premium and employer stipends</li>\n 	<li>Reconciliation of employer monthly billings</li>\n</ul>', 'Retiree Products and Services', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '175-autosave-v1', '', '', '2016-06-29 08:47:17', '2016-06-29 12:47:17', '', 175, 'https://insightba.net/175-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
 (238, 2, '2016-06-30 10:36:40', '2016-06-30 14:36:40', 'Recognizing the need for a more efficient, cost-effective way to deliver a higher level of third party administration services and benefit consulting, President &amp; CEO Howard Lancaster formed Insight Benefit Administrators.\r\nAlong with complete TPA services Insight Benefit Administrators offers benefits audit/consulting services.  Leveraging our substantial expertise and experience, we can provide an objective review of plan administration, employee communications, compliance and more.\r\nOur mission:\r\nFor our clients :\r\nWe strive to:\r\n•    actively seek feedback from your, our clients, your employees and the agent/broker community\r\n•    continually evaluate product and service alternatives\r\n•    to educate you and your employees\r\nThe Insight team approaches each covered member with caring, educational support and  experience while maintaining the highest ethical standards and confidentiality.\r\nFor our employees:\r\nInsight promotes freedom of opinion, ideas and expression; provides opportunities for professional growth; and is strives to maintain essential work-life balance.\r\nFor the communities we serve: Our social mission is to provide educational and financial support for pediatric dental care to underinsured and uninsured children.  (To learn more contact howardl@insightba.net.)\r\nWe welcome your questions and suggestions. Use our Contact Us page to reach any one of us.', 'About Us', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '2-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-06-30 10:36:40', '2016-06-30 14:36:40', '', 2, 'https://insightba.net/2-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
 (178, 1, '2016-06-14 12:12:21', '2016-06-14 16:12:21', '<span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">Recognizing the need for a more efficient, cost-effective way to deliver a higher level of third party administration services and benefit consulting, <span style="font-family: Arial;">President &amp; CEO Howard Lancaster formed</span><strong> Insight Benefit Administrators.</strong> </span>\r\n\r\nAlong with complete TPA services Insight Benefit Administrators offers benefits audit/consulting services.  <span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">Leveraging our substantial expertise and experience, we can provide an objective review of plan administration, employee communications, compliance and more.</span>\r\n\r\nOur mission:\r\n\r\n<em>For our clients :  </em>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">We strive to:</span>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">actively seek feedback from your, our clients, your employees and the agent/broker community</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">continually evaluate product and service alternatives</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">to educate you and your employees</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">The Insight team approaches each covered member with caring, educational support and  experience while maintaining the highest ethical standards and confidentiality.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><em>For our employees:</em> </span>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">Insight promotes freedom of opinion, ideas and expression; provides opportunities for professional growth; and is strives to maintain essential work-life balance.</span>\r\n\r\n<em>For the communities we serve: </em>Our social mission is to provide educational and financial support for pediatric dental care to underinsured and uninsured children.  (To learn more contact howardl@insightba.net.)\r\n\r\nWe welcome your questions and suggestions. Use our <a title="Contact Us" href="/contact/">Contact Us</a> page to reach any one of us.', 'About Us', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '2-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-06-14 12:12:21', '2016-06-14 16:12:21', '', 2, 'https://insightba.net/2-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
 (181, 1, '2016-06-15 10:51:44', '2016-06-15 14:51:44', 'Post-65 Medical Coverage\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>standard Medicare Supplement Coverage</li>\r\n 	<li>Medicare Advantage Coverage</li>\r\n 	<li>Group Retiree Insurance Medical Coverage (GRIP)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nPost-65 Prescription Coverage\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Employer Group Waiver Plan (EGWP) Coverage</li>\r\n 	<li>Fully Insured Group Prescription Coverage (PDP)</li>\r\n 	<li>Group Retiree Insurance Prescription (GRIP) Coverage</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nBilling and Enrollment\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Enrollment in Medical/Rx/Voluntary Programs</li>\r\n 	<li>Collection of retiree premium and employer stipends</li>\r\n 	<li>Reconciliation of employer monthly billings</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Retiree Products and Services', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '175-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-06-15 10:51:44', '2016-06-15 14:51:44', '', 175, 'https://insightba.net/175-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
 (182, 1, '2016-06-15 10:57:27', '2016-06-15 14:57:27', 'IBA evaluated carriers throughout the country that offer either replacement coverage to traditional Medicare Parts A &amp; B coverage or options to coordinate with traditional Medicare Parts A &amp; B coverage.  We chose to partner with carriers that demonstrate flexibility in plan design, provide top-notch service and deliver lower than average medical trend renewals. We formed partnerships with carriers that lower retiree premiums and stretch employer stipend dollars.\r\n\r\nIBA has access to several fully insured medical coverage carriers and options including:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Group medical coverage down to 2 lives</li>\r\n 	<li>Copay and coinsurance options</li>\r\n 	<li>Dental, Hearing and Vision options</li>\r\n 	<li>Holistic benefit options, such as Acupuncture and Chiropractic care</li>\r\n 	<li>Choice of Age Banded or Composite rating</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nImportant to those who travel, these programs offer freedom of choice with no network limitations and national access to providers and hospitals.', 'Post-65 Medical Products', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'post-65-medical-products', '', '', '2016-06-29 08:55:29', '2016-06-29 12:55:29', '', 175, 'https://insightba.net/?page_id=182', 0, 'page', '', 0),
 (183, 1, '2016-06-15 10:57:27', '2016-06-15 14:57:27', 'IBA has evaluated multiple carriers nationwide that offer either replacement coverage to traditional Medicare Parts A &amp; B coverage or options to coordinate with traditional Medicare Parts A &amp; B coverage. We’ve chosen to partner with carriers that demonstrate flexibility in plan design, provide top-notch service and deliver lower than average medical trend renewals. In addition, we’ve chosen partnerships that lower retiree premiums and stretch employer stipend dollars.\r\n\r\nIBA has access to several fully insured medical coverage carriers and options including:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Group medical coverage down to 2 lives</li>\r\n 	<li>Copay and coinsurance options</li>\r\n 	<li>Dental, Hearing and Vision options</li>\r\n 	<li>Holistic benefit options, such as Acupuncture and Chiropractic care</li>\r\n 	<li>Choice of Age Banded or Composite rating</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nImportant to those who travel, these programs offer freedom of choice with no network limitations and national access to providers and hospitals.', 'Post-65 Medical Products', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '182-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-06-15 10:57:27', '2016-06-15 14:57:27', '', 182, 'https://insightba.net/182-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
 (184, 1, '2016-06-15 10:58:09', '2016-06-15 14:58:09', 'IBA has evaluated multiple carriers nationwide that offer either replacement coverage to traditional Medicare Parts A &amp; B coverage or options to coordinate with traditional Medicare Parts A &amp; B coverage.  We’ve chosen to partner with carriers that demonstrate flexibility in plan design, provide top-notch service and deliver lower than average medical trend renewals. In addition, we’ve chosen partnerships that lower retiree premiums and stretch employer stipend dollars.\r\n\r\nIBA has access to several fully insured medical coverage carriers and options including:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Group medical coverage down to 2 lives</li>\r\n 	<li>Copay and coinsurance options</li>\r\n 	<li>Dental, Hearing and Vision options</li>\r\n 	<li>Holistic benefit options, such as Acupuncture and Chiropractic care</li>\r\n 	<li>Choice of Age Banded or Composite rating</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nImportant to those who travel, these programs offer freedom of choice with no network limitations and national access to providers and hospitals.', 'Post-65 Medical Products', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '182-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-06-15 10:58:09', '2016-06-15 14:58:09', '', 182, 'https://insightba.net/182-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
 (185, 1, '2016-06-15 10:59:21', '2016-06-15 14:59:21', 'IBA vetted access to fully insured carriers offering multiple prescription coverage options and varying formularies. From stand-alone prescription drug programs (PDP) to integrated medical and prescription drug coverage (MAPD), we  canvassed the market -- comparing pricing and formulary coverage to ensure the best price with the least disruption for your retirees. Popular alternatives including Employer Group Waiver Plans (EGWP) are easier for employers and retirees to understand and navigate.\r\n\r\nPrescription coverage carriers and options include:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Group prescription coverage down to 2 lives</li>\r\n 	<li>National retail network and mail order options</li>\r\n 	<li>Multiple prescription copay and coinsurance options</li>\r\n 	<li>Formulary alternatives for both basic and enhanced benefits (e.g. lifestyle drugs)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nThese programs offer retirees national retail networks and mail order options for convenience and portability.', 'Post-65 Prescription Products', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'post-65-prescription-drug-products', '', '', '2016-06-29 08:57:49', '2016-06-29 12:57:49', '', 175, 'https://insightba.net/?page_id=185', 0, 'page', '', 0),
 (186, 1, '2016-06-15 10:59:21', '2016-06-15 14:59:21', 'IBA has vetted access to fully insured carriers offering multiple prescription coverage options and varying formularies. From stand-alone prescription drug programs (PDP) to integrated medical and prescription drug coverage (MAPD), we have canvassed the market comparing pricing and formulary coverage to ensure the best price with the least disruption for your retirees. Popular alternatives including Employer Group Waiver Plans (EGWP) are easier for employers and retirees to understand and navigate.\r\n\r\nPrescription coverage carriers and options include:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Group prescription coverage down to 2 lives</li>\r\n 	<li>National retail network and mail order options</li>\r\n 	<li>Multiple prescription copay and coinsurance options</li>\r\n 	<li>Formulary alternatives for both basic and enhanced benefits (e.g. lifestyle drugs)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nThese programs offer retirees national retail networks and mail order options for convenience and portability.', 'Post-65 Prescription Drug Products', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '185-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-06-15 10:59:21', '2016-06-15 14:59:21', '', 185, 'https://insightba.net/185-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
 (187, 1, '2016-06-15 11:00:46', '2016-06-15 15:00:46', 'Educational Assistance Simplifies Enrollment (EASE). IBA’s approach to enrollment ensures effective communications for employers and retirees. We work with you to create custom messaging for your group of retirees. We make open enrollment materials easy to understand, making the retiree benefit experience a positive one.\r\n\r\nE.A.S.E. components for a successful enrollment include:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Developing easy to understand welcome kits and enrollment instructions for Post-65 retirees</li>\r\n 	<li>Creating proactive enrollment instructions for Pre-65 retirees aging into the programs</li>\r\n 	<li>Identifying and emphasizing important plan design changes</li>\r\n 	<li>Holding informational retiree open enrollment sessions</li>\r\n 	<li>Tracking and monitoring outstanding enrollments</li>\r\n 	<li>Providing monthly billing for medical/prescription/voluntary benefits to retirees in paper form or via ACH</li>\r\n 	<li>Retiree advocacy navigating medical and prescription coverage questions or issues</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nThe EASE protocols ensure that you and your retirees have the necessary tools to enroll timely and provide consistency in handling ongoing adds/changes/terminations.', 'Billing and Enrollment Support', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'billing-and-enrollment-support', '', '', '2016-06-29 09:02:14', '2016-06-29 13:02:14', '', 175, 'https://insightba.net/?page_id=187', 0, 'page', '', 0),
 (188, 1, '2016-06-15 11:00:46', '2016-06-15 15:00:46', 'Educational Assistance Simplifies Enrollment (EASE). IBA’s approach to enrollment ensures effective communications for employers and retirees. IBA works with the employer to create messaging that is customized to their group of retirees. IBA makes open enrollment material easy to understand making the retiree benefit experience a positive one.\r\n\r\nE.A.S.E. components for a successful enrollment include:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Developing easy to understand welcome kits and enrollment instructions for Post-65 retirees</li>\r\n 	<li>Creating proactive enrollment instructions for Pre-65 retirees aging into the programs</li>\r\n 	<li>Identifying and emphasizing important plan design changes</li>\r\n 	<li>Holding informational retiree open enrollment sessions</li>\r\n 	<li>Tracking and monitoring outstanding enrollments</li>\r\n 	<li>Providing monthly billing for medical/prescription/voluntary benefits to retirees in paper form or via ACH</li>\r\n 	<li>Retiree advocacy navigating medical and prescription coverage questions or issues</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nThe EASE protocols ensure the employers and retirees have the necessary tools to enroll timely and provide consistency in handling ongoing adds/changes/terminations.', 'Billing and Enrollment Support', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '187-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-06-15 11:00:46', '2016-06-15 15:00:46', '', 187, 'https://insightba.net/187-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
 (189, 1, '2016-06-16 10:33:03', '2016-06-16 14:33:03', '<strong>- insert document howard is reviewing here - </strong>\n\nnew content:\n\nSelf Funding with Insight Benefit Administrators has many advantages:\n<ul>\n 	<li>We administer the plan to suit your particular needs</li>\n 	<li>We bring you with the best of the best benefits providers</li>\n 	<li>You  have more control and flexibility with benefits offered</li>\n 	<li>Administrative costs are lower</li>\n 	<li>You don\'t have to  pay premium taxes</li>\n 	<li>You don\'t have to offer state mandated benefits LINK</li>\n 	<li>You\'re free from many ACA fees LINK DETAILS</li>\n 	<li>Your risk is managed with Stop Loss insurance LINK</li>\n 	<li>You have a clearer understanding of how your dollars are spent</li>\n</ul>\nWhile there are more administrative decisions for you to make, we\'re here to guide you.', 'About Self Funding', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '147-autosave-v1', '', '', '2016-06-16 10:33:03', '2016-06-16 14:33:03', '', 147, 'https://insightba.net/147-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
 (190, 1, '2016-06-16 10:24:59', '2016-06-16 14:24:59', '<strong>- insert document howard is reviewing here - </strong>\r\n\r\nnew content\r\n\r\nSelf Funding with Insight Benefit Administrators has many advantages:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>We administer the plan to suit your particular needs</li>\r\n 	<li>We bring you with the best of the best benefits providers</li>\r\n 	<li>You  have more control and flexibility with benefits offered</li>\r\n 	<li>Administrative costs are lower</li>\r\n 	<li>You don\'t have to  pay premium taxes</li>\r\n 	<li>You don\'t have to offer state mandated benefits LINK</li>\r\n 	<li>You\'re free from many ACA fees LINK DETAILS</li>\r\n 	<li>Your risk is managed with Stop Loss insurance LINK</li>\r\n 	<li>You have a clearer understanding of how your dollars are spent</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nWhile there are more administrative decisions for you to make, we\'re here to guide you.', 'About Self Funding', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '147-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-06-16 10:24:59', '2016-06-16 14:24:59', '', 147, 'https://insightba.net/147-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
 (191, 1, '2016-06-16 10:33:43', '2016-06-16 14:33:43', '<strong>- insert document howard is reviewing here - </strong>\r\n\r\nnew content:\r\n\r\nSelf Funding with Insight Benefit Administrators has many advantages:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>We administer the plan to suit your particular needs</li>\r\n 	<li>We bring you with the best of the best benefits providers</li>\r\n 	<li>You  have more control and flexibility with benefits offered</li>\r\n 	<li>Administrative costs are lower</li>\r\n 	<li>You don\'t have to  pay premium taxes</li>\r\n 	<li>You don\'t have to offer state mandated benefits LINK</li>\r\n 	<li>You\'re free from many ACA fees LINK DETAILS</li>\r\n 	<li>Your risk is managed with Stop Loss insurance LINK</li>\r\n 	<li>You have a clearer understanding of how your dollars are spent</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nWhile there are more administrative decisions for you to make, we\'re here to guide you.\r\n\r\nIt\'s important to understand that Self Funding is a <em>long term strategy</em>.  WHY\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'About Self Funding', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '147-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-06-16 10:33:43', '2016-06-16 14:33:43', '', 147, 'https://insightba.net/147-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
