 (222, 1, '2016-06-29 08:56:54', '2016-06-29 12:56:54', 'IBA vetted access to fully insured carriers offering multiple prescription coverage options and varying formularies. From stand-alone prescription drug programs (PDP) to integrated medical and prescription drug coverage (MAPD), we  canvassed the market -- comparing pricing and formulary coverage to ensure the best price with the least disruption for your retirees. Popular alternatives including Employer Group Waiver Plans (EGWP) are easier for employers and retirees to understand and navigate.\n\nPrescription coverage carriers and options include:\n<ul>\n 	<li>Group prescription coverage down to 2 lives</li>\n 	<li>National retail network and mail order options</li>\n 	<li>Multiple prescription copay and coinsurance options</li>\n 	<li>Formulary alternatives for both basic and enhanced benefits (e.g. lifestyle drugs)</li>\n</ul>\nThese programs offer retirees national retail networks and mail order options for convenience and portability.', 'Post-65 Prescription Products', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '185-autosave-v1', '', '', '2016-06-29 08:56:54', '2016-06-29 12:56:54', '', 185, 'https://insightba.net/185-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
 (223, 1, '2016-06-29 08:57:49', '2016-06-29 12:57:49', 'IBA vetted access to fully insured carriers offering multiple prescription coverage options and varying formularies. From stand-alone prescription drug programs (PDP) to integrated medical and prescription drug coverage (MAPD), we  canvassed the market -- comparing pricing and formulary coverage to ensure the best price with the least disruption for your retirees. Popular alternatives including Employer Group Waiver Plans (EGWP) are easier for employers and retirees to understand and navigate.\r\n\r\nPrescription coverage carriers and options include:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Group prescription coverage down to 2 lives</li>\r\n 	<li>National retail network and mail order options</li>\r\n 	<li>Multiple prescription copay and coinsurance options</li>\r\n 	<li>Formulary alternatives for both basic and enhanced benefits (e.g. lifestyle drugs)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nThese programs offer retirees national retail networks and mail order options for convenience and portability.', 'Post-65 Prescription Products', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '185-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-06-29 08:57:49', '2016-06-29 12:57:49', '', 185, 'https://insightba.net/185-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
 (224, 1, '2016-06-29 09:01:54', '2016-06-29 13:01:54', 'Educational Assistance Simplifies Enrollment (EASE). IBA’s approach to enrollment ensures effective communications for employers and retirees. We work with you to create custom messaging for your group of retirees. We make open enrollment materials easy to understand, making the retiree benefit experience a positive one.\n\nE.A.S.E. components for a successful enrollment include:\n<ul>\n 	<li>Developing easy to understand welcome kits and enrollment instructions for Post-65 retirees</li>\n 	<li>Creating proactive enrollment instructions for Pre-65 retirees aging into the programs</li>\n 	<li>Identifying and emphasizing important plan design changes</li>\n 	<li>Holding informational retiree open enrollment sessions</li>\n 	<li>Tracking and monitoring outstanding enrollments</li>\n 	<li>Providing monthly billing for medical/prescription/voluntary benefits to retirees in paper form or via ACH</li>\n 	<li>Retiree advocacy navigating medical and prescription coverage questions or issues</li>\n</ul>\nThe EASE protocols ensure that you and your retirees have the necessary tools to enroll timely and provide consistency in handling ongoing adds/changes/terminations.', 'Billing and Enrollment Support', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '187-autosave-v1', '', '', '2016-06-29 09:01:54', '2016-06-29 13:01:54', '', 187, 'https://insightba.net/187-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
 (225, 1, '2016-06-29 09:01:57', '2016-06-29 13:01:57', 'Educational Assistance Simplifies Enrollment (EASE). IBA’s approach to enrollment ensures effective communications for employers and retirees. We work with you to create custom messaging for your group of retirees. We make open enrollment materials easy to understand, making the retiree benefit experience a positive one.\r\n\r\nE.A.S.E. components for a successful enrollment include:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Developing easy to understand welcome kits and enrollment instructions for Post-65 retirees</li>\r\n 	<li>Creating proactive enrollment instructions for Pre-65 retirees aging into the programs</li>\r\n 	<li>Identifying and emphasizing important plan design changes</li>\r\n 	<li>Holding informational retiree open enrollment sessions</li>\r\n 	<li>Tracking and monitoring outstanding enrollments</li>\r\n 	<li>Providing monthly billing for medical/prescription/voluntary benefits to retirees in paper form or via ACH</li>\r\n 	<li>Retiree advocacy navigating medical and prescription coverage questions or issues</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nThe EASE protocols ensure that you and your retirees have the necessary tools to enroll timely and provide consistency in handling ongoing adds/changes/terminations.', 'Billing and Enrollment Support', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '187-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-06-29 09:01:57', '2016-06-29 13:01:57', '', 187, 'https://insightba.net/187-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
 (226, 2, '2016-06-29 11:04:56', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', 'Auto Draft', '', 'auto-draft', 'open', 'open', '', '', '', '', '2016-06-29 11:04:56', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', 0, 'https://insightba.net/?p=226', 0, 'post', '', 0),
 (227, 2, '2016-07-07 09:55:19', '2016-07-07 13:55:19', 'To begin, let us define a few terms for you:\r\n\r\nASO - Administrative Services Only\r\n\r\nSelf-Funding -\r\n\r\nTPA  .......\r\n\r\n<strong>  </strong>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nSelf Funding with Insight Benefit Administrators has many advantages:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>We administer the plan to suit your particular needs</li>\r\n 	<li>We bring you with the best of the best benefits providers</li>\r\n 	<li>You  have more control and flexibility with benefits offered</li>\r\n 	<li>Administrative costs are lower</li>\r\n 	<li>You don\'t have to  pay premium taxes</li>\r\n 	<li>You don\'t have to offer state mandated benefits LINK</li>\r\n 	<li>You\'re free from many ACA fees LINK DETAILS</li>\r\n 	<li>Your risk is managed with Stop Loss insurance LINK</li>\r\n 	<li>You have a clearer understanding of how your dollars are spent</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nWhile there are more administrative decisions for you to make, we\'re here to guide you.\r\n\r\nIt\'s important to understand that Self Funding is a <em>long term strategy</em>.  WHY\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'About Self Funding', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '147-autosave-v1', '', '', '2016-07-07 09:55:19', '2016-07-07 13:55:19', '', 147, 'https://insightba.net/147-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
 (228, 2, '2016-06-29 12:43:11', '2016-06-29 16:43:11', 'To begin, let us define a few terms for you:\r\n\r\nASO - Administrative Services Only\r\n\r\nSelf-Funding -\r\n\r\nTPA  .......\r\n\r\n<strong>  </strong>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nSelf Funding with Insight Benefit Administrators has many advantages:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>We administer the plan to suit your particular needs</li>\r\n 	<li>We bring you with the best of the best benefits providers</li>\r\n 	<li>You  have more control and flexibility with benefits offered</li>\r\n 	<li>Administrative costs are lower</li>\r\n 	<li>You don\'t have to  pay premium taxes</li>\r\n 	<li>You don\'t have to offer state mandated benefits LINK</li>\r\n 	<li>You\'re free from many ACA fees LINK DETAILS</li>\r\n 	<li>Your risk is managed with Stop Loss insurance LINK</li>\r\n 	<li>You have a clearer understanding of how your dollars are spent</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nWhile there are more administrative decisions for you to make, we\'re here to guide you.\r\n\r\nIt\'s important to understand that Self Funding is a <em>long term strategy</em>.  WHY\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'ASO 101 - Self Funding for Beginners', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '147-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-06-29 12:43:11', '2016-06-29 16:43:11', '', 147, 'https://insightba.net/147-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
